# Exploration: df

## Rounds
  round 0: 85 isolated cumulative, 7 identical in round (discovery)
  round 1: 85 isolated cumulative, 7 identical in round (refinement)

## Distinguished: 16/16 flags
  16 solo (unique behavior)

Aliases: -B = --block-size, -H = --si, -P = --portability, -T = --print-type, -a = --all, -h = --human-readable, -i = --inodes, -l = --local, -t = --type, -x = --exclude-type

## Solo (unique behavior)
  --no-sync  # do not invoke sync before getting usage info (default)
